    "Within the OCTOPUS module, high-precision multiplication tasks are executed by five links (L0-L4), with passive beam splitter trees facilitating splitting and combining operations on each link.",
    "The reference link at the bottom supports coherent detection, enabling the realization of negative dot product operations and providing the bias term in the linear neuron.",
